data.description: Gorgeous brick and stone adorned family home nestled in Resort of Eagle Mountain with a golf course view on the 9th hole! 5 bed 3 and a half bath, w a mediaroom. New carpeting, updated grey paint throughout, tiled floors in wet areas. Kitchen is made for a family with double SS ovens, gas cooktop, ss dishwasher, and gorgeous granite counters. Butlers pantry and a massive walk in pantry with shelving. LR is spacious with vaulted ceilings and views out in to the peaceful backyard over looking the golf course. The master is secluded w trayed ceiling and on suite bath w soaking tub, dual vanities, sep shower and WIC. Wrought iron and wood staircase leads up to the second floor that includes 4 bedrooms a bath and a media room.
data.whatILove: Spacious home with wonderful updates throughout and a highly sought after golf course view!
